snippet.title: Amber Heard MOCKS NEW Judge Over Johnny Depp's Win!
snippet.description:
FAIRFAX, Va. (CN) — Johnny Depp’s lawsuit accusing his ex-wife Amber Heard of defamation enters its third year in court with a ruling that the actress must turn over drafts of an editorial she published in The Washington Post.   Let me know what you think!
